  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This early post-marketing study is an observational, prospective and descriptive study of
      patients receiving daclatasvir for the treatment of Chronic Hepatitis C at participating
      sentinel sites for the CNFV in Mexico.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
